{
  "stem": "1479.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a little bit unbelievable too because we, the, the survivors, after years of surviving those horrible death camps, we still came out from those death camps with hope, determination to start a new life.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We even expected that the world will embrace us with compassion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And yet, we were confronted by the whole world, after the liberation, with this belief-- we were even accused of exaggeration, that something like that could not happen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this, after a while, we could understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because who would or could understand?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something like that happen in the middle of civilization?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the 20th century?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we saw the world had no compassion, no sympathy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We relied on our own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And only through hard, very hard work and determination, we built a new life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we arrived in this-- by the way, our first child was born in Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Few people are aware or they do realize that the problem for us, the survivors, never ended.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of the women who survived the camps could not bear children because for whatever the Nazis did, either with those chemicals in our food or whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's why I said, we were very fortunate that we decided and we started to build a new life and start a new family.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Many, many women needed medical attention and could bear children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "However, a lot could never return to a normal life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Many survivors who were liberated, for them, it was too late.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They could-- there were those who could not cope with life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had to be institutionalized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were many problems what we faced right after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The only thing what I can say, and to me, it's very important.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
